nodeList.name: Facial Expression Detection
nodeList.description: Detect facial expressions of people using this effect. To detect facial expression more than one face, assign a Face Expression Detection node to each face in the scene. It can detect up to five facial expressions.

nodeList.name: Color Space Converter
nodeList.description: Convert a color from one color space to another. It supports RGBA to HSLA, RGBA to HSVA, HSVA to RGBA, and HSLA to RGBA.

property.value: Convert a color from one color space to another. It supports RGBA to HSLA, RGBA to HSVA, HSVA to RGBA, and HSLA to RGBA.

nodeList.name: Combine
nodeList.description: Pack inputs into a vector or color data. The number of inputs depends on the selected data type. And the outputs are in the same order as they were inputted. Supported types: Vec2, Vec3, Vec4, and Color.
